summary:
So here’s a mega collection of @kingdomofkitten’s Ikariverse!
First is when Ikari meets his two friends, Kuuma and Nezumi for...
body:
So here’s a mega collection of @kingdomofkitten’s Ikariverse!

First is when Ikari meets his two friends, Kuuma and Nezumi for the first time.

Next is when he shows his new friends to his dad, building a crib for new sister and his mom, who is pregnant with his new sister.

Third, we have Bezumi getting picked up by he older brother, Haru.

Next up we have Retsuko during her pregnancy, when the sound of chewing gives her a spitting headache. The funny thing is, Doriyakis are actually soft. Last picture is the aftermath of the incident.

summary: Hello there everyone! I know it has been a while and I am sorry about that. I have been swamped with commission work and college...
caption:
Hello there everyone!

I know it has been a while and I am sorry about that. I have been swamped with commission work and college has been kicking my ass but hopefully now that summer is here I will have time to do some requests.

I also wanna wish my followers a happy pride month! I did this quick edit of Retsuko with the new lesbian flag and I think that it looks really good. ^^

I will use this one in the future as I have heard some very nasty things about the creator of the all pink one.

Thank you all for sticking around for so long!

-Mod Dorito

summary: Aggretsuko Season 2 Is Coming to Netflix on June 14
title: Aggretsuko Season 2 Is Coming to Netflix on June 14
body:
Everyone’s favorite metalhead red panda will be back on Netflix this month!

Netflix recently announced on Twitter that Aggretsuko’s second season has a release date: June 14, 2019!

Everyone’s favorite overworked, underpaid, karaoke-loving red panda secretary is back and is rage-ier than ever before! Even though she is still surrounded by all of her friends, Retsuko will now be faced with more incompetent coworkers, the pressure of getting married and starting a family,…
